Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.23,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,Body improvement!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.57,0:00:05.74,Default,All,0,0,0,,Fight on! Fight on! Fight on! Fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.44,0:00:10.03,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}Psychic powers don't make a man appealing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.95,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, in order to change myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.41,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}I joined the Body Improvement Club.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.04,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,Body improvement!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.04,0:00:20.21,Default,All,0,0,0,,Fight on! Fight on! Fight on!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.71,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,Body improvement!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.63,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Fight... on... Fight... on...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.01,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.55,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,He must be anemic.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.14,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Sh-Showwy......
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.99,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,There's definitely something wrong with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.99,0:02:16.41,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,{\q2}Who would choose the\NBody Improvement Club in that situation?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.66,Default,Inu,0,0,0,,Well, let's not dwell on the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.66,Default,Inu,0,0,0,,Come on. It's your turn, President Kurata.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.54,0:02:24.08,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.50,Default,All,0,0,0,,Ah, Musashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.79,0:02:29.38,Default,All,0,0,0,,{\q2}Thank you so much for \Nletting us use this room!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.26,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,You don't have to grovel...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.51,0:02:35.30,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,All we want the room for is to store our equipment.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.76,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.14,0:02:39.89,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,Oh, Kageyama passed out.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.27,Default,Cap,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you watch over him?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.31,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Seriously, dude.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.07,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Why did you join the Body Improvement Club?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.32,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I've never been the most athletic guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.70,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,And I'm a really slow runner.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.70,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's because I've relied on my \Npsychic powers for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.83,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Huh? What kind of excuse is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.25,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you actually have psychic powers, \NI'd love to see them, jeez.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.68,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Is that enough for you to believe me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.93,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,This is heavy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.43,Default,Inu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously? He could only bend spoons before!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.44,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Please! Help me make my dream come true!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.48,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Believe it or not...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.11,0:03:36.86,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,{\q2}My dream is to contact and interact \Nwith extraterrestrial lifeforms!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.41,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,{\q2}At first, I followed a guidebook\Nand tried it out, but it didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.04,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, I was just lazing around...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.50,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.50,0:03:49.33,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,I've got my big break!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.63,0:03:53.05,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Mob, let's research telepathy together,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.05,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,{\q2}seek a new life, and boldly go\Nwhere no man has gone before!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.76,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Actually, I've got weight lifting to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.89,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Wait, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.22,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm burning with passion here.\NWhy are you so ice-cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.10,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I've finally found something that I want to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.06,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,What, putting on muscle?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.90,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,But you have psychic powers...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.31,0:04:16.07,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}Actually, maybe I should say I want to\Nbecome more appealing as a man.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.57,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,You want to be popular, Mob?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.66,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.74,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Well, you won't be.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.62,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Even if you gain muscle, you won't become popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.25,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.25,0:04:30.33,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Th-Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.96,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Read girls' minds using telepathy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.30,Default,Tome,0,0,0,,Then you'll be super popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.05,Default,Reig,0,0,0,,What? Telepathy?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.76,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't really do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.31,Default,Reig,0,0,0,,I can hear the voices of spirits, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.89,Default,Reig,0,0,0,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.31,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I was just wondering...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.69,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Is there someone whose mind you want to read?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.07,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,A girl, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.15,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,My, my, Mob...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.07,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,You're so easy to read.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.82,0:05:04.91,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Well, every middle school boy wants to be popular,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.66,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,so there's no need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.08,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Even I want to be popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.84,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like I want to be popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.26,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to get close to Tsubomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.59,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,Pardon me, young man.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.30,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,Something must be troubling you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.35,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,You aren't laughing or smiling.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.35,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.10,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.85,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,You're worried about your studies, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.69,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.69,0:05:35.11,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,Of course not. It's not your studies...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.11,0:05:38.11,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,Yes, it must be hard dealing with family issues.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.36,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't have any.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.36,0:05:44.37,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,{\q2}Of course you don't. \NIt must be your health... No...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.49,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,It's about love.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.29,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.54,0:05:54.58,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,If you want to resolve your troubles, come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.29,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Actually, I have to head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.46,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,You'll be popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.88,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.30,0:06:09.81,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,{\q2}I belong to a brand-new religious order\Nthat came into existence last month.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.60,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Religious order?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.81,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,It's called (LOL).
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.69,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,Founded by our leader, Dimple,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.69,0:06:20.57,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,{\q2}it's the happiest and trendiest\Ngathering of the century!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.57,0:06:25.82,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,{\q2}Dimple has the mysterious power \Nto make anyone laugh immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.70,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,So, how do I become popular?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.58,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't be so hasty.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.25,0:06:38.29,Default,Mask,0,0,0,,(LOL) is in no way a suspicious group.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.59,0:06:42.72,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow, there are a lot of people.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.47,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if they all want to be popular, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, are you new, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.26,0:06:49.85,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.22,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Then get on stage.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.31,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.19,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.65,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.65,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Heave-ho, heave-ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.98,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea what's going on anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.90,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Huh? Mob?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.74,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\q2}Do you recognize me? \NI'm Mezato from your class.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.04,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, I've never talked to her before.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.37,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Did they lure you in?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.58,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.58,Alt,Some,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.58,Default,Some,0,0,0,,It's Dimple!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.17,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.72,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Are you laughing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.10,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Are you sufficiently warmed up now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.39,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Why don't we take off those masks, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.65,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.82,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You're all smiling so brightly.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.66,Default,Man,0,0,0,,What a creepy bunch...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.91,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.91,0:08:01.17,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}Today, we have three new \Nsmilemates joining us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.17,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Give them a big hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.80,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.92,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Hey, don't...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.92,0:08:11.39,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}In order to accept happiness, \Nyou must set your hearts free.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.39,0:08:15.47,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,But your hearts are locked up.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.73,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}See? It's completely obvious \Nwhy you're unhappy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.73,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You aren't laughing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.57,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Laugh. If you laugh even in pain,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.69,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,your hearts will be unlocked!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.83,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,And once they have been set free,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.83,0:08:36.58,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}your hearts will have the ability to\Naccept happiness as it comes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.58,0:08:40.71,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}In order to have a happy life,\Nyou must have a hearty laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.21,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,That is the teaching of (LOL).
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.21,0:08:48.34,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\q2}Hah. How I {\i1}wish{\i0} people could\Nbe happy just by laughing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.68,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Who might this be?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.68,Default,Some,0,0,0,,We found him on a park bench.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.47,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,How sad. A victim of the recession!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.35,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,It's no wonder you've lost your smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.23,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,But worry not!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.48,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Let's put on this smile mask and fix that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.98,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.48,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.82,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,This is our way of saving you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.82,0:09:12.70,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,We just want you to smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.62,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}No resistance.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.66,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Lastly, the girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.50,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,It appears that you have something to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.96,0:09:28.17,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Religious order (LOL), established last month?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.76,0:09:32.51,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\q2}You managed to attract this many \Nfollowers in just one month?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.68,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,I don't believe that!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.68,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Oh? And you are...?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.77,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,I work for Salt Middle School's newspaper!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.68,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,I'm Mezato from Class 2-1!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.02,0:09:43.56,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm reporting on the bad rumor\Nconcerning you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.06,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Bad rumor?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.32,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\q2}That you're using group hypnosis to\Nbrainwash and force people into joining.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.45,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}She has the nerve to say that \Nafter sneaking in by herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.70,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Splendid.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.33,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Let me provide you with proof, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.99,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}Please take a look at\Nthe gentleman from earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.33,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,A few minutes ago, he was a very sad man.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.09,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,What a wonderful smile!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.71,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,How funny...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.59,Alt,Meza,0,0,0,,{\move(960,937,960,1023,901,1301)\i1}He's laughing? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.59,0:10:14.18,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,He has now truly grasped happiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.10,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,What do you think, young lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.35,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}True, they didn't do anything bad...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.35,Default,Some,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll find a job.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.90,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}But something's still off.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.86,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something strange in the air here...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.86,0:10:33.65,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\q2}This story is a bit too much\Nfor me to handle,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.16,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,so if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.12,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.62,0:10:42.37,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}You infiltrated (LOL) and\Ndoubted our smiles for no reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.62,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.62,0:10:47.13,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,I won't write about you in the school paper.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.13,0:10:50.88,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}That is not enough!\NIt won't ease our hard feelings!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.38,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,We won't let you leave until you laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.76,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,I-I don't really feel like laughing right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.39,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\q2}And if I forced myself to right now,\Nit wouldn't be sincere.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.39,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Start with a smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.02,0:11:08.27,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to lie to myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.40,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.69,0:11:12.69,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.78,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Huh? I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.03,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.87,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.45,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sparkle!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.21,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Look at that magnificent smile!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.58,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.46,0:11:27.25,Default,Some,0,0,0,,{\an8}You seem completely different now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.67,Default,Yon,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.67,Default,Some,0,0,0,,{\an8}What a gleaming smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.67,0:11:29.21,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.71,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.71,0:11:36.47,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're all smiling, and it feels really nice...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.47,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no! I don't really want to smile!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.06,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone save me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.98,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.44,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mob!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.15,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,So the theme here is smiling and happiness?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.19,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}It doesn't have anything to do \Nwith being popular?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.94,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,May I leave now, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.53,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.53,0:11:59.49,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{\q2}He looked troubled on his way home \Nfrom school, so I brought him here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.53,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,It seems he's having trouble with love.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.33,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I'm not really troubled, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.46,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not smiling!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.00,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Are you telling me that\Nthe smile mask didn't work?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.46,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Huh? He's not smiling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.63,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.38,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.97,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}Do you plan to live the rest \Nof your life with that face?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.30,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You are missing out on life!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.52,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}My dad said that\N"people who've never smoked before
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.23,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,are missing out on half of their lives."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.60,0:12:32.23,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}It made me realize that everyone has\Na different idea of "missing out."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.23,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.57,0:12:40.41,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}(LOL) is the start line for me to become\Na religious figure for all of humanity!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.74,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let this trip me up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.58,0:12:48.25,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}I just want you to know\Nhow wonderful it is to smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.75,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.00,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}Th-Then would you like to \Nplay a game before you leave?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.00,0:12:57.51,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}A staring contest. You'll have a staring \Ncontest with three of my smile leaders.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.51,0:13:01.84,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}You'll all drink milk,\Nand the first to laugh loses.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.01,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.68,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mob, this is a trap!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.48,0:13:18.49,Default,Ref,0,0,0,,Are you ready? If you laugh, you lose.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.78,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you accept the challenge?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.53,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mob loves milk.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.45,Default,Ref,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.79,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.88,0:13:37.13,Default,Ref,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.92,0:13:41.88,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.64,Default,Smile,0,0,0,,Those two are pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.89,Default,Smile,0,0,0,,{\q2}With my smiling powers, I'll throw\Nthat boy into a smiley maelstrom...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.14,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.15,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forcing them to laugh all the time backfired!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.03,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I won, so I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.03,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.45,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You'll have to face me now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.24,0:14:04.87,Default,Some,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.45,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Dimple is going to face him himself?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.45,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will not let you win.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.45,0:14:12.46,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will make you spit out that milk!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.46,0:14:15.21,Default,Ref,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.59,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}That milk...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.47,0:14:26.47,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}clearly had something mixed in.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.31,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,He laughed!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.60,Default,Some,0,0,0,,He laughed!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.81,0:14:30.60,Alt,Some,0,0,0,,He spit it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.89,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Nothing less from our Dimple!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.31,Default,Some,0,0,0,,He saved another!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.31,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I'm starting to have fun now...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.73,0:14:43.45,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I... didn't laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.20,Default,Meza,0,0,0,,Huh? My smile...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.54,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Wait, why am I here again?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.50,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Because it's so much fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.46,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You just...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.01,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}No, he couldn't possibly have\Nundone my hypnosis.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.68,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why can't I make him laugh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.10,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no choice. I'll have to go all out.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.85,0:15:18.40,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}Everyone! Let us save\Nthe laughter trapped within him!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.65,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}If he stayed this way,\NI'd feel too sorry for him!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.40,Default,Some,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.40,Alt,Some,0,0,0,,Dimple!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.74,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Let us laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.11,Alt,Mob,0,0,0,,Hey, wait. I...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.11,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Smile and live a good life!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.11,0:15:31.12,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,See? You don't have a single enemy here,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.87,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,so what exactly are you fighting?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.00,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Get a clue.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.92,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,{\t(438,0,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Hey, Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.71,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Why do you always look so bored?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.76,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.22,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,If you're bored, go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.22,0:15:48.97,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,But I'm not.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.18,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,You're the only one who's not laughing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.10,Default,Tsu,0,0,0,,Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.48,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Tsubomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.56,Default,Tsub,0,0,0,,Get a clue.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.82,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,I will show you my true power.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.37,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Now, laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.49,Default,Some,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.00,Default,Some,0,0,0,,It's Dimple's divine power!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.38,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.26,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.84,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Why aren't you laughing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.76,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Are you saying my powers don't work on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.76,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Laugh! Come on, laugh, you brat! Laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.14,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. He has psychic powers, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.52,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Are you a corpse?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.94,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Your powers can't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.98,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I don't hate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.90,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I just couldn't, even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.70,0:16:53.37,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I don't mean anything bad by it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.66,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... He...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.79,0:17:01.12,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You must not have emotions, brat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.12,0:17:04.25,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}They mentioned that you were \Nhaving troubles with love.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.71,0:17:09.30,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}With a personality like that, you won't\Nbe able to laugh with the girl you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.30,0:17:13.39,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}The feelings of people resonate\Nwith one another, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.55,0:17:17.14,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\a6}But you're unable to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:21.40,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You can't cry together, or even be moved.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.44,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You'll be forever alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.86,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,I'll give you one last chance...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.86,0:17:31.91,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.66,0:17:38.16,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make me laugh with your psychic powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.17,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You... I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.92,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,So you have similar powers...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.42,0:17:51.68,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}I thought I picked a peaceful religious order\Nthat'd cause the least bloodshed,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.97,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,but you're in my way, brat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.97,0:17:57.43,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'll have to get rid of the outsider \Nthat brings chaos to this environment.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.64,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. You're not a person.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.73,0:18:05.31,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}Thank goodness the one who said\Nsomething as horrible as "get a clue"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.82,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,was an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.94,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,My followers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.99,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Do not let him leave alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.70,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\i1}A strong commanding signal...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.88,Default,Tsub,0,0,0,,Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.75,Default,Tsub,0,0,0,,Get a clue.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.80,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is an esper present here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.22,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}A grade-schooler called \N"Mob" by those around him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.85,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though he's blessed with tremendous powers,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.85,0:18:44.85,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}he's subconsciously always avoided \Ntrying to display those powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.40,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}As he grew,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.40,0:18:52.40,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}he gradually realized\Nhow dangerous his powers were.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.28,0:18:57.95,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}When people are unable to act \Nor do as they please,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.95,0:19:01.20,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}their emotions come to a halt.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.62,0:19:08.46,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Mob hasn't realized that his aversion to\Nusing his powers has become a complex.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.55,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}The emotions that are locked away\Ndeep inside Mob's heart
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.01,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}expand little by little.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.43,0:19:18.64,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}However, there is a limit to \Nhow much his emotions can take
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.68,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}before leaking out and going wild.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.47,0:19:27.02,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}And now, an emotion was swirling \Nabout like a torrent, trying to go past the limit.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.94,0:19:34.95,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.24,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rage.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.70,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,To think that you were such a powerful esper...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.20,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,No wonder the smile mask didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.71,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Mask? So there was a trick to that, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.50,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}I didn't even notice \Nbecause it was so weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.21,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.47,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}If the policy of your religion \Nis to kill the outsiders,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.80,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,come at me with everything you've got.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.47,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,That might be easier than making me laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.14,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,"Come at me with everything you've got"?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.35,0:20:13.23,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}Two seconds is plenty of time \Nto make you disappear, brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.70,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You're just livestock without emotions!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.66,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Don't try to act like you're actually angry!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.16,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,How about you cry next?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.17,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Oho, how flashy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.51,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.31,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.27,0:20:49.27,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,{\q2}I never thought I'd have to \Nfight with my full powers...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.52,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,You may be the real thing, brat,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.19,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,but this is where you die!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.53,0:20:57.24,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.99,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.54,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.21,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,They came out upon your request.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.46,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,These are my emotions.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.59,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,This is what happens if I let them show.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.09,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,A-Are you some kind of monster?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.97,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.81,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Wraither Beam!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.10,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Yes! A direct hit!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.94,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,The number of fights I've endured
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.94,0:21:36.90,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,is what decides the victor and loser here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.28,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I'm... {\alpha&HFF&}terrible.{\alpha&H00&}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.45,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,I'm... terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.50,0:21:52.25,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.72,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,You want to be able to get a clue?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.22,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Social skills like that are beyond you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.22,0:22:09.02,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}The only ones capable of them \Nhave common sense and experience.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.52,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}On the other hand, your \Nexistence itself makes no sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.60,0:22:16.27,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you bummed out about that now?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.15,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,{\q2}Because I'm such a downer, \NI ruined a whole bunch of people's fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.86,0:22:26.20,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Huh? Why do you have to be like them?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.78,0:22:29.49,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,You're the protagonist of your own life.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.58,0:22:35.38,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,That whole group is now gone because of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.96,0:22:38.04,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,All they were doing was laughing...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.88,0:22:42.63,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, your inability to get a clue \Nis pretty destructive.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.89,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,What happened? You can tell me all about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.47,0:22:52.39,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Huh? What were we...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.39,0:22:54.31,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Dimple is passed out.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.40,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Did he always look like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.31,0:23:01.65,Default,Some,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wasn't he trying to make some \Nboy smile, but he wouldn't?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.78,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Who was that boy?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.78,0:23:04.90,Default,Some,0,0,0,,Let's look for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.49,Default,Some,0,0,0,,He might be the true messenger of God.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.53,0:23:13.41,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I see... so typical mind control.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.83,0:23:16.92,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}That's not salvation. He was just \Nhaving them depend on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.84,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's a popular con \Nbased on crowd psychology,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.84,0:23:24.76,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}but considering you're hyper dense,\Nit didn't work on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.55,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Which means, Mob,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.55,0:23:33.85,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}today you happened to save some people\Nthat only you could have saved.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.27,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Shige, wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.27,0:23:43.11,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're going to be late.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.03,0:23:48.95,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.95,0:23:51.20,Default,Dimp,0,0,0,,Isn't it a lovely morning, Partner?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.79,0:23:59.13,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}Mob gets dragged into an idiotic \Nevent run by idiots for idiots.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.13,0:24:01.92,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,{\q2}The one that then appears before him\Nis a violent yet handsome guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.92,0:24:03.46,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Mob?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.46,0:24:05.34,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Next time on Mob Psycho 100 Episode 4:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.47,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,"Idiots Only Event ~Kin~"
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.97,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,DVD? That's an excellent decision!
